<LanguageData>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_CitadelEngineer.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 專門負責維護城堡的防禦和基礎設施，確保驕傲的據點免受所有威脅。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_CitadelEngineer.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_CitadelEngineer.title>城堡工程師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_CitadelEngineer.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_CitadelEngineer.titleShort>工程師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_CitadelEngineer.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Cook.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 維持城堡的飲食，為騎士和文士準備豐盛的飯菜，並為驕傲隊提供的每頓飯都鼓舞士氣。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Cook.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Cook.title>驕傲廚師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Cook.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Cook.titleShort>廚師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Cook.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Demolitions_Expert.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 專門從事爆炸物、清理瓦礫和摧毀敵方防禦工事，以便驕傲隊在首都荒原的行動。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Demolitions_Expert.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Demolitions_Expert.title>爆破專家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Demolitions_Expert.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Demolitions_Expert.titleShort>拆除</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Demolitions_Expert.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Field_Instructor.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 在武器操作、戰術和生存方面訓練新兵，塑造下一代里昂驕傲戰士。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Field_Instructor.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Field_Instructor.title>現場講師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Field_Instructor.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Field_Instructor.titleShort>講師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Field_Instructor.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Mechanic.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 維護傲慢號的載具和動力裝甲，確保每台機器都做好隨時戰鬥的準備。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Mechanic.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Mechanic.title>驕傲機械師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Mechanic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Mechanic.titleShort>機械</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Mechanic.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Power_Armor_Operator.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 掌握了動力裝甲的使用和維護，領導對超級變種人的進攻，並以無與倫比的韌性保護里昂的驕傲利益。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Power_Armor_Operator.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Power_Armor_Operator.title>動力裝甲操作員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Power_Armor_Operator.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Power_Armor_Operator.titleShort>裝甲操作員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Power_Armor_Operator.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Quartermaster.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 管理驕傲隊的軍械庫，向騎士和文士分發武器和補給品，並確保在生存之戰中不浪費任何東西。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Quartermaster.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Quartermaster.title>軍需</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Quartermaster.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Quartermaster.titleShort>軍需</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Quartermaster.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Recon_Specialist.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 擅長偵察敵人陣地和收集情報，並經常冒險深入敵方領土以確保驕傲隊的戰術優勢。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Recon_Specialist.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Recon_Specialist.title>偵察專家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Recon_Specialist.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Recon_Specialist.titleShort>偵察</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Recon_Specialist.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Salvage_Team_Leader.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 帶領探險隊進入危險的廢墟，為驕傲隊的持續生存回收寶貴的技術和資源。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Salvage_Team_Leader.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Salvage_Team_Leader.title>打撈隊長</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Salvage_Team_Leader.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Salvage_Team_Leader.titleShort>打撈者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Salvage_Team_Leader.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Scout_Leader.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 帶領偵察隊穿過華盛頓特區的廢墟，繪製安全路線並識別威脅，然後才能攻擊驕傲隊。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Scout_Leader.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Scout_Leader.title>童軍領袖</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Scout_Leader.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Scout_Leader.titleShort>童軍領袖</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Scout_Leader.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Wasteland_Defender.description>經過多年的訓練，[PAWN_nameDef] 成為了一名成熟的騎士，在 DC 的廢墟中巡邏並保衛定居點免受襲擊者和變種人的侵害。 [PAWN_pronoun] 在里昂驕傲隊中因勇敢和戰術技巧而享有盛譽。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Wasteland_Defender.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Wasteland_Defender.title>荒地衛士</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Wasteland_Defender.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Wasteland_Defender.titleShort>後衛</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Wasteland_Defender.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Lyons_Pride_Veteran.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 與傳奇的里昂之傲並肩作戰，面對首都廢土的最大威脅。 [PAWN_pronoun] 因 [PAWN_possessive] 的勇氣和對驕傲隊理想堅定不移的忠誠而受到尊重。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Lyons_Pride_Veteran.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Lyons_Pride_Veteran.title>里昂的驕傲老將</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Lyons_Pride_Veteran.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Lyons_Pride_Veteran.titleShort>驕傲老兵</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Lyons_Pride_Veteran.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Outcast_Hunter.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 的任務是追蹤和對抗流亡者，執行里昂長老的願景並保護驕傲組織的團結。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Outcast_Hunter.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Outcast_Hunter.title>被遺棄的獵人</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Outcast_Hunter.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Outcast_Hunter.titleShort>被遺棄的獵人</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Outcast_Hunter.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Archivist.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 奉獻了 [PAWN_possessive] 一生來保存驕傲的歷史，並對每一項回收的技術和知識進行編目。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Archivist.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Archivist.title>檔案管理員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Archivist.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Archivist.titleShort>檔案管理員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Archivist.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Communications_Officer.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 維持巡邏隊和城堡之間的無線電聯繫，協調任務並為荒地中的驕傲隊傳遞重要訊息。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Communications_Officer.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Communications_Officer.title>傳訊官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Communications_Officer.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Communications_Officer.titleShort>通訊官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Communications_Officer.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Diplomat.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 代表里昂之傲與廢土定居點和敵對派系進行談判，建立聯盟並確保資源。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Diplomat.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Diplomat.title>驕傲外交官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Diplomat.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Diplomat.titleShort>外交官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Diplomat.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Field_Researcher.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 前往荒地研究變異的動植物群，為獅群提供寶貴的科學見解和生存知識。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Field_Researcher.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Field_Researcher.title>實地研究員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Field_Researcher.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Field_Researcher.titleShort>實地研究員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Field_Researcher.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Researcher.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 專注於開發新的治療方法和藥物，利用戰前知識和荒地發現來治癒驕傲隊的傷者。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Researcher.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Researcher.title>醫學研究員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Researcher.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Researcher.titleShort>醫學研究員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Researcher.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Specialist.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 致力於拯救生命，成為醫學專家，治療受傷的里昂驕傲成員並研究先進的治療技術。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Specialist.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Specialist.title>醫療專家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Specialist.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Specialist.titleShort>軍醫</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Specialist.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Technology_Seeker.description>身為抄寫員，[PAWN_nameDef] 在荒原上搜尋失落的知識和戰前技術，為里昂驕傲檔案館記錄每一項發現。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Technology_Seeker.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Technology_Seeker.title>科技探索者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Technology_Seeker.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Technology_Seeker.titleShort>科技探索者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Technology_Seeker.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 早年花費 [PAWN_possessive] 幫助驕傲檔案管理員保存和研究戰前文件，了解歷史和記錄保存的重要性。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.title>檔案員助理</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.titleShort>檔案管理員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Bunker_Born.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 在城堡的堅固城牆內出生長大。從很小的時候起，[PAWN_pronoun] 就了解了紀律、秩序的價值以及技術在重建文明中的重要性，這是里昂驕傲的一部分。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Bunker_Born.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Bunker_Born.title>地堡誕生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Bunker_Born.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Bunker_Born.titleShort>地堡誕生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Bunker_Born.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Canteen_Apprentice.description>雖然驕傲隊迴避奢侈品，但長老們承認，一頓像樣的飯菜可以鼓舞士氣。作為一名鄉紳，[PAWN_nameDef]展現了烹飪天賦，並經常幫助食堂工作人員。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Canteen_Apprentice.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Canteen_Apprentice.title>食堂學徒</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Canteen_Apprentice.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Canteen_Apprentice.titleShort>食堂學徒</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Canteen_Apprentice.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Field_Medic.description>被分配到醫療艙後，[PAWN_nameDef] 學習了基本的急救和戰場分診，為 [PAWN_objective] 準備應對荒地戰鬥的嚴酷現實，這是里昂驕傲的一部分。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Field_Medic.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Field_Medic.title>戰地軍醫鄉紳</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Field_Medic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Field_Medic.titleShort>戰地醫療兵</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Field_Medic.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Junior_Medic.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 協助 Pride 醫護人員進行基本急救，並學會了照顧傷員，培養了穩定的雙手和富有同情心的心。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Junior_Medic.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Junior_Medic.title>初級軍醫</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Junior_Medic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Junior_Medic.titleShort>初級軍醫</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Junior_Medic.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.description>[PAWN_nameDef] learned responsibility and teamwork by helping organize meals and supplies in the Pride's mess hall, ensuring everyone was fed and accounted for.</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.title>Mess Hall Steward</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.titleShort>混亂管家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Messenger.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 被信任在整個城堡內傳遞訊息和物資，了解可靠性和快速思維在驕傲行動中的重要性。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Messenger.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Messenger.title>鄉紳信使</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Messenger.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Messenger.titleShort>信差</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Messenger.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.description>從很小的時候起，[PAWN_nameDef]就對傲慢號標誌性的動力裝甲著迷。 [PAWN_pronoun] 花了無數時間學習維護並最終操作這些技術奇蹟。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.title>動力裝甲實習生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.titleShort>鎧甲實習生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scout_In_Training.description>從很小的時候起，[PAWN_nameDef]就被教導如何在華盛頓特區的廢墟中航行，向驕傲斥候學習潛行、觀察和生存技能。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scout_In_Training.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scout_In_Training.title>童軍訓練中</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scout_In_Training.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scout_In_Training.titleShort>見習童子軍</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scout_In_Training.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 被一個 Pride Scribe 選為早期指導，學習閱讀、寫作和分析古代文本和圖表。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.title>文士的學生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.titleShort>文士的學生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 對戰前遺跡著迷，花了 [PAWN_possessive] 青年時期協助驕傲文士恢復古代技術，學習知識和耐心的價值。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.title>科技學徒</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.titleShort>科技學徒</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.titleShort>
